{"tid":1747741,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"關於今次區選想幫大家打定個底","createTime":"2019-11-23T10:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T14:02:39.000Z","uid":16949,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"faea9fd7b9f5dc28462876b293c3378bead2bb63","tid":1747741,"uid":16949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:59:02.000Z","msg":"見到咁多post講區選<br />\n有人話區選冇用, 有人話區選係民意既較量<br />\n我見到區選都未完已經大量分化post<br />\n我個人認為<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">區選係要盡可能做<br />\n但唔好睇到係endgame</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n經過咗咁多個年<br />\n當初港共已經玩唔少制度暴力<br />\n覺得你會贏或者顯示到真民意咪DQ你 (e.g. 陳浩天, 梁天琦, 黃之鋒)<br />\n佢今次有恃無恐去繼續搞區選就必然有手段贏<br />\n種票, 票箱失蹤一段時間, 冒充其他人投票, 甚至係一啲我地未諗過既方式去造票<br />\n所以唔好覺得區選係大哂係真民意<br />\n然後泛民一大敗就開始捉鬼同分化<br />\n我地一路以黎贏既係靠團結不分化<br />\n求下你地唔好再犯5年前既錯誤<br />\n即使建制大勝或大敗都好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好分化, 唔好割蓆</span></strong></span><br />\n我地可能會輸區選<br />\n但如果我地因為輸區選而分裂, 就會輸埋場運動<br />\n相反, 如果我地最後要贏<br />\n就應該繼續做以下既事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>1. 拉走啲齋屌但又冇建設性既post</strong></span><br />\n屌唔係問題, 畀埋你認為邊度可以做得更好既地方先係屌得有價值<br />\n齋屌發洩既post麻煩大家用不推文回覆同負評幫手拉走<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>2. 繼續做你覺得對運動有幫助既事</strong></span><br />\n都係執天琦口水尾<br />\n唱歌既繼續唱, 鳩叫既繼續叫, 裝修既繼續裝, 舉旗既繼續舉<br />\n塞鐵既繼續塞, 搞工會既繼續搞, 有想法就去做<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">3. 將行動轉地下化</span></strong><br />\n過咗咁多個月大家都開始明白靜靜地贏既道理<br />\n唔好咩都擺上黎呃正評<br />\n保護手足先係最重要<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n區選唔係endgame<br />\n結果係點都好<br />\n唔好放棄, 黎明必會到來<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"84dd11a1a2c1eef61033ac458c35376edd9c8799","tid":1747741,"uid":16949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:01:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563e896686e17604f7d6de73b33ca5baecb22d75","tid":1747741,"uid":16949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:03:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7debbdbdb6e38361c8ab75199a5d1f4ec071e06a","tid":1747741,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:04:02.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n唔係公投<br />\n未贏架<br />\n對家隨時做馬做到前未有咁仆街<br />\n當贏後只會玩死自己"},{"pid":"94842a1833f7268050eaec5da6be112a60aab2a8","tid":1747741,"uid":16949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7debbdbdb6e38361c8ab75199a5d1f4ec071e06a","tid":1747741,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:04:02.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n唔係公投<br />\n未贏架<br />\n對家隨時做馬做到前未有咁仆街<br />\n當贏後只會玩死自己"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:05:09.000Z","msg":"講得啱<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">區選唔係ENDGAME</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"99e9b7c4c85a75badbe055d91628bca582485037","tid":1747741,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:05:16.000Z","msg":"贏唔到議席都好 票數一定要壓到性贏建制<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c139aeff8cbc5ed92ef5ccbac8b30e13d601c6","tid":1747741,"uid":16949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:06:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地可能會輸區選<br />\n但如果我地因為輸區選而分裂, 就會輸埋場運動</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7cd074415c9d210d2debe71fabb3ea22362b548f","tid":1747741,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:06:55.000Z","msg":"除咗投票 仲可以做多樣野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747531</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"18e437e75f4bfa19d8c492e1f1cdb91f6a7f0462","tid":1747741,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0265c225dc0faf41609b66c337cacd4675b4b7","tid":1747741,"uid":16949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:14:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b6764c1ca407cfc37156ec26128afe867848aaa","tid":1747741,"uid":336561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb37fde7cf4997253728df6a002d28568390876","tid":1747741,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ff65bad37b9e44de77351f123c947a075b47ea","tid":1747741,"uid":16949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:33:04.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"0e6ae6a1e0acb4478c2105812585e1b02c8db7b6","tid":1747741,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94388efdafd12f8b4453026e45402ba702fa0edd","tid":1747741,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:40:59.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6723c11e36a7a6427a020bb87f69c80bb0598cd9","tid":1747741,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa02fc2f4bc4521ad29915a3c41decae5999dde8","tid":1747741,"uid":185121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:47:53.000Z","msg":"輸咗唔代表政府無視我哋既訴求係等於合理<br />\n少數人又好多數人都好, 所有人民既訴求都應該被尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食屎政府咪諗住種票種贏咗就冇鑊要孭"},{"pid":"88e5d9b670b4975fcedc0dcff0eb5fd0573a3cc2","tid":1747741,"uid":238374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:48:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n聽朝7點起身後 <br />\n大聲向窗鳩叫<br />\n「早晨呀！夠鐘起身投票啦！」<br />\n屋企係藍既就落樓叫 其他手足請自動join<br />\n目標係成條邨叫三次<br />\n叫醒埋其他手足起身<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2a6f09555b2f2aadaf54341e5fe8db8de4eb306e","tid":1747741,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6c53ae83e589d49e89b8e7b8dfc573b7b312cf","tid":1747741,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:49:42.000Z","msg":"好撚驚d人吹到今次係end game <br />\n同佢地講唔好諗一個一直以黎食民生為主既選舉做end game <br />\n一陣又比人話我帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d180c02508c6ecdb335fdb15f0e1b6fc73721d","tid":1747741,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8affd5697e62fa394c65f3f33be4301a3478bd","tid":1747741,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:19:41.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有無發現。<br />\n我地好似忽略咗班少數族裔選民？<br />\n先唔講選舉有無用<br />\n但作為社會一分子，我地唔係應該俾足夠既選舉資訊啲少數族裔，去選自己心儀既候選人？<br />\n<br />\n我地好似有樣嘢無做？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747382\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747382</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fa15f8c576741404af6ad3b4bbcd642be492ec87","tid":1747741,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:20:13.000Z","msg":"啱, 區選只係一個回合<br />\n並唔係成場仗"},{"pid":"c2ea2507fbc7032a66f82385c918eb51e8630a66","tid":1747741,"uid":90421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b7406d848d4816880d0bbabe17b2c2fb100ee4","tid":1747741,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}